1
00:00:16,800 --> 00:00:17,140
Mom,

2
00:00:18,380 --> 00:00:19,400
where are you going?

3
00:00:20,099 --> 00:00:20,740
Let go!

4
00:00:22,119 --> 00:00:23,240
Your eyes

5
00:00:23,880 --> 00:00:25,640
are just like your father's.

6
00:00:28,780 --> 00:00:30,039
Why?

7
00:01:06,320 --> 00:01:07,740
Hey, it's raining hard.

8
00:01:07,740 --> 00:01:09,439
You'll get wet and sick.

9
00:01:14,040 --> 00:01:15,280
Get lost.

10
00:01:29,819 --> 00:01:32,579
Dirty water hurts the wound.

11
00:03:08,699 --> 00:03:09,419
Are you awake,

12
00:03:10,840 --> 00:03:13,680
or just thinking of a new scam?

13
00:03:16,580 --> 00:03:17,759
I'm glad to see you as soon as I wake up,

14
00:03:19,340 --> 00:03:20,340
but in this way.

15
00:03:22,939 --> 00:03:25,219
Zhou Xubai, Department of Mathematics, Qingdao University,

16
00:03:25,699 --> 00:03:27,020
Chief Information Officer of Lanze Capital.

17
00:03:27,580 --> 00:03:29,259
How do you feel about

18
00:03:30,020 --> 00:03:30,780
replacing someone else?

19
00:03:39,199 --> 00:03:41,620
It seems that you know me inside out.

20
00:03:43,639 --> 00:03:46,580
How much of your reliance and tenderness

21
00:03:46,979 --> 00:03:49,840
is real and how much is fake?

22
00:03:51,159 --> 00:03:53,800
Zhi Mei, you're a better actress than me.

23
00:03:59,580 --> 00:04:00,740
Why is Wu Xi?

24
00:04:05,319 --> 00:04:07,860
What does his disappearance have to do with you?

25
00:04:09,340 --> 00:04:10,340
What do you think?

26
00:04:17,639 --> 00:04:18,800
Answer me!

27
00:04:23,580 --> 00:04:24,660
If I say

28
00:04:25,759 --> 00:04:28,560
I did it to protect you,

29
00:04:31,019 --> 00:04:32,040
will you believe me?

30
00:04:32,720 --> 00:04:34,100
Protect me?

31
00:04:38,500 --> 00:04:40,579
With lies and deceit?

32
00:04:51,860 --> 00:04:52,579
Take good care of him.

33
00:04:54,439 --> 00:04:55,980
Don't let him leave the room.

34
00:04:57,100 --> 00:04:57,800
Yes.

35
00:05:11,759 --> 00:05:13,160
The master is no longer here.

36
00:05:13,360 --> 00:05:14,579
You don't need to come here anymore.

37
00:05:16,180 --> 00:05:17,319
This is your separation pay.

38
00:05:23,399 --> 00:05:24,259
Go.

39
00:05:24,259 --> 00:05:24,959
Yes.

40
00:05:27,899 --> 00:05:29,399
Zhang Wei,

41
00:05:29,639 --> 00:05:31,300
please help me

42
00:05:31,920 --> 00:05:32,920
nullify that will.

43
00:05:34,220 --> 00:05:35,079
Xiaomei.

44
00:05:35,319 --> 00:05:36,259
Should we file a formal complaint

45
00:05:36,259 --> 00:05:38,199
regarding Zhou Xubai's

46
00:05:38,699 --> 00:05:40,779
suspected identity theft?

47
00:05:42,740 --> 00:05:43,800
Not for now.

48
00:05:44,579 --> 00:05:46,860
I want to handle this myself.

49
00:05:48,740 --> 00:05:49,379
Meimei,

50
00:05:50,579 --> 00:05:52,079
what should we do with these surveillance hard drives?

51
00:05:52,579 --> 00:05:54,279
There might be many records inside.

52
00:05:55,579 --> 00:05:56,579
Should we destroy them?

53
00:06:04,819 --> 00:06:06,579
Zhou Xubai refuses to tell us his purpose.

54
00:06:07,439 --> 00:06:10,379
Maybe there's other evidence inside.

55
00:06:20,959 --> 00:06:21,500
Doctor,

56
00:06:21,959 --> 00:06:24,240
was I the only injured person in that fire?

57
00:06:25,540 --> 00:06:26,819
There was another one who was seriously injured.

58
00:06:27,560 --> 00:06:28,439
He's a disabled person.

59
00:06:29,000 --> 00:06:31,319
His left leg prostheses were burned together.

60
00:06:32,240 --> 00:06:33,120
A disabled person?

61
00:06:38,279 --> 00:06:39,620
[The one died in the fire]

62
00:06:39,620 --> 00:06:41,220
[wasn't the motorcycle rider.]

63
00:06:41,360 --> 00:06:43,560
[He must be still out there. Zhimei is in danger.]

64
00:06:46,500 --> 00:06:48,699
Doctor, my wound still hurts a bit.

65
00:06:48,699 --> 00:06:49,459
Could you check it again?

66
00:07:00,139 --> 00:07:00,759
It's fine.

67
00:07:00,899 --> 00:07:02,300
The nurse will re-bandage it in a bit.

68
00:07:02,579 --> 00:07:03,560
Okay, thank you.

69
00:07:50,180 --> 00:07:51,980
Have they grown any bigger?

70
00:07:52,240 --> 00:07:52,980
Yes.

71
00:08:02,060 --> 00:08:02,660
Honey,

72
00:08:03,259 --> 00:08:04,660
will you always be with me?

73
00:08:04,660 --> 00:08:07,639
Of course, I will always be with you.

74
00:08:34,699 --> 00:08:35,279
Doctor,

75
00:08:35,579 --> 00:08:36,779
is something wrong with Zhou Xubai?

76
00:08:37,839 --> 00:08:38,339
Zhi Mei,

77
00:08:39,220 --> 00:08:39,839
listen to me.

78
00:08:40,580 --> 00:08:41,919
You are in danger now.

79
00:08:46,759 --> 00:08:47,259
Leave home.

80
00:08:47,799 --> 00:08:48,360
Hurry up.

81
00:09:05,679 --> 00:09:06,019
Zhi Mei,

82
00:09:06,580 --> 00:09:06,960
it's me.

83
00:09:06,960 --> 00:09:07,500
Let me go.

84
00:09:08,200 --> 00:09:08,740
Let me go.

85
00:09:10,419 --> 00:09:11,500
I'm finally back.

86
00:09:12,059 --> 00:09:12,720
Wu Xi,

87
00:09:27,259 --> 00:09:28,519
I finally found you.
